<!-- Definition and symptoms -->
'''消化道出血'''（{{lang-en|gastrointestinal bleed (GI bleed)}}、{{lang|en|gastrointestinal hemorrhage}}）是[[口腔|口腔]]至[[直腸|直腸]]之間任何部位的消化道出血<ref name="NIH2014">{{cite web|title=Bleeding in the Digestive Tract|url=http://www.niddk.nih.gov/health-information/health-topics/digestive-diseases/bleeding-in-the-digestive-tract/Pages/facts.aspx|accessdate=6 March 2015|date=September 17, 2014|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150221091014/http://www.niddk.nih.gov/health-information/health-topics/digestive-diseases/bleeding-in-the-digestive-tract/Pages/facts.aspx|archivedate=2015-02-21|dead-url=yes|website=www.niddk.nih.gov}}</ref>。當短時間內大量出血時，可能導致的症狀包含[[嘔血|嘔血]]、{{le|Coffee ground vomiting||吐黑血}}、[[便血|便血]]，或{{le|黑便|Melena}}。長期的小量出血可能導致[[缺鐵性貧血|缺鐵性貧血]]，而造成[[疲倦|疲倦]]或[[心絞痛|心絞痛]]<ref name="Kim2014">{{Cite journal|title=Diagnosis of gastrointestinal bleeding: A practical guide for clinicians|url=http://www.wjgnet.com/2150-5330/full/v5/i4/467.htm|last=Kim|first=Bong Sik Matthew|date=2014|journal=World Journal of Gastrointestinal Pathophysiology|issue=4|doi=10.4291/wjgp.v5.i4.467|volume=5|pages=467|language=en|issn=2150-5330|pmc=PMC4231512|pmid=25400991|access-date=2021-03-01|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205121447/https://www.wjgnet.com/2150-5330/full/v5/i4/467.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其他症狀則包含[[腹痛|腹痛]]、[[呼吸困難|呼吸困難]]，或[[昏厥|昏厥]]<ref name="NIH2014" /><ref name=Kim2014/>。有時候小量出血並不會有任何症狀產生<ref name="Kim2014" />。

<!-- Causes and diagnosis -->
消化道出血主要分為兩種類型，分別為[[上消化道出血|上消化道出血]]與{{le|下消化道出血|Lower gastrointestinal bleeding}}<ref name="EBMED2004">{{cite journal|title=Gastrointestinal Bleeding: An Evidence-Based ED Approach To Risk Stratification|url=http://www.ebmedicine.net/topics.php?paction=showTopic&topic_id=75|last=Westhoff|first=John|date=March 2004|journal=Emergency Medicine Practice|accessdate=2016-06-05|issue=3|volume=6|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130722192754/http://www.ebmedicine.net/topics.php?paction=showTopic&topic_id=75|archivedate=2013-07-22|deadurl=no}}</ref>。[[胃及十二指腸潰瘍|胃及十二指腸潰瘍]]、或者[[肝硬化|肝硬化]]和[[肝癌|肝癌]]容易合併的{{le|食道靜脈曲張|esophageal varices}}，也都可能成為導致上消化道出血的原因<ref name="Epi2008">{{Cite journal|title=Epidemiology of acute upper gastrointestinal bleeding|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18346679|last=van Leerdam|first=M. E.|date=2008|journal=Best Practice & Research. Clinical Gastroenterology|issue=2|doi=10.1016/j.bpg.2007.10.011|volume=22|pages=209–224|issn=1521-6918|pmid=18346679|access-date=2021-03-01|archive-date=2021-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211217231927/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18346679/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而下消化道出血的原因，則通常是[[痔瘡|痔瘡]]、癌症及[[炎症性腸病|炎症性腸病]]造成的<ref name="EBMED2004" />。過去病史、[[理學檢查|理學檢查]]和血液檢查，都可以幫助診斷腸胃道出血。少量的出血可以透過{{tsl|en|fecal occult blood||糞便潛血反應}}來判斷，而[[內視鏡|內視鏡]]則可以定位上消化道和下消化道的出血區域。在不清楚病情的情況下，[[醫學影像|醫學影像]]也是一項非常有用的工具<ref name="Kim2014" />。

<!-- Treatment -->
初步的治療主要關注在{{le|復甦急救|resuscitation}}上如[[靜脈注射|靜脈注射]]與[[輸血|輸血]]<ref name="Overall2011">{{Cite journal|title=The overall approach to the management of upper gastrointestinal bleeding|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/21944416|last=Jairath|first=Vipul|last2=Barkun|first2=Alan N.|date=2011-10|journal=Gastrointestinal Endoscopy Clinics of North America|issue=4|doi=10.1016/j.giec.2011.07.001|volume=21|pages=657–670|issn=1558-1950|pmid=21944416|access-date=2021-03-01|archive-date=2021-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211218000636/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/21944416/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，通常要[[血紅蛋白|血紅蛋白]]量以低於70-80g/L以下才會採取輸血急救<ref name="Wang2013">{{Cite journal|title=Impact of more restrictive blood transfusion strategies on clinical outcomes: a meta-analysis and systematic review|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24331453|last=Salpeter|first=Shelley R.|last2=Buckley|first2=Jacob S.|date=2014-02|journal=The American Journal of Medicine|issue=2|doi=10.1016/j.amjmed.2013.09.017|volume=127|pages=124–131.e3|issn=1555-7162|pmid=24331453|last3=Chatterjee|first3=Saurav|access-date=2021-03-01|archive-date=2020-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925113126/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24331453/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在某些案例中會使用[[氫離子幫浦阻斷劑|氫離子幫浦阻斷劑]]、{{le|等體制素|octreotide}}與[[抗细菌药|抗生素]]<ref name="PPI2007">{{Cite journal|title=Systematic reviews of the clinical effectiveness and cost-effectiveness of proton pump inhibitors in acute upper gastrointestinal bleeding|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18021578|last=Leontiadis|first=G. I.|last2=Sreedharan|first2=A.|date=2007-12|journal=Health Technology Assessment (Winchester, England)|issue=51|doi=10.3310/hta11510|volume=11|pages=iii–iv, 1–164|issn=1366-5278|pmid=18021578|last3=Dorward|first3=S.|last4=Barton|first4=P.|last5=Delaney|first5=B.|last6=Howden|first6=C. W.|last7=Orhewere|first7=M.|last8=Gisbert|first8=J.|last9=Sharma|first9=V. K.|access-date=2021-03-01|archive-date=2020-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200420011554/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18021578/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="N2010">{{Cite journal|title=Medical management of variceal hemorrhage|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/20691388|last=Cat|first=Tram B.|last2=Liu-DeRyke|first2=Xi|date=2010-09|journal=Critical Care Nursing Clinics of North America|issue=3|doi=10.1016/j.ccell.2010.02.004|volume=22|pages=381–393|issn=1558-3481|pmid=20691388|access-date=2021-03-01|archive-date=2021-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211217230123/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/20691388/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Chavez2011">{{Cite journal|title=Meta-analysis: antibiotic prophylaxis for cirrhotic patients with upper gastrointestinal bleeding - an updated Cochrane review|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/21707680|last=Chavez-Tapia|first=N. C.|last2=Barrientos-Gutierrez|first2=T.|date=2011-09|journal=Alimentary Pharmacology & Therapeutics|issue=5|doi=10.1111/j.1365-2036.2011.04746.x|volume=34|pages=509–518|issn=1365-2036|pmid=21707680|last3=Tellez-Avila|first3=F.|last4=Soares-Weiser|first4=K.|last5=Mendez-Sanchez|first5=N.|last6=Gluud|first6=C.|last7=Uribe|first7=M.|access-date=2021-03-01|archive-date=2021-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207213517/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/21707680/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。如果其他方法都無效，則可能可以推測為食道靜脈屈張，並以{{le|食道狹窄氣球擴張術|esophageal ballon}}治療<ref name="EBMED2004" />。一旦發現有消化道出血的狀況發生，建議在24小時內進行[[上消化道內視鏡|上消化道內視鏡]]以及{{le|大腸鏡|Colonoscopy}}照影，並進行治療<ref name="Overall2011" />。

<!-- Epidemiology and prognosis -->
上消化道出血比下消化道出血要常見<ref name="EBMED2004" />。上消化道出血每年每十萬人約發生50到150次<ref name="Red2010">{{Cite journal|title=Red cell transfusion for the management of upper gastrointestinal haemorrhage|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/20824851|last=Jairath|first=Vipul|last2=Hearnshaw|first2=Sarah|date=2010-09-08|journal=The Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews|issue=9|doi=10.1002/14651858.CD006613.pub3|pages=CD006613|issn=1469-493X|pmid=20824851|last3=Brunskill|first3=Susan J.|last4=Doree|first4=Carolyn|last5=Hopewell|first5=Sally|last6=Hyde|first6=Chris|last7=Travis|first7=Simon|last8=Murphy|first8=Michael F.|access-date=2021-03-01|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926225335/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/20824851/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。下消化道出血則是每年每十萬人約發生20到30次<ref name="EBMED2004" />。在[[美國|美國]]，消化道出血造成每年30萬次住院人次。消化道出血致死率為 5% 到30% 之間<ref name="Kim2014" /><ref name="Wang2013" />。消化道出血的風險在男性較高，也隨著年紀而上升<ref name="EBMED2004" />。

==上消化道出血==
從口腔、食道、胃到十二指腸，其中任一器官發生病變而導致出血，稱為上消化道出血，俗稱'''胃出血'''。

上消化道出血常見的原因包括：消化性潰瘍、糜爛性胃炎、食道或胃靜脈瘤、食道胃接合處黏膜撕裂、全身性疾病、和其他。

==下消化道出血==
十二指腸以下到直腸部分的出血稱為下消化道出血。

下消化道出血常見的原因包括：痔瘡、結腸炎、出血性直腸潰瘍、大腸癌、良性息肉、感染性腸炎、憩室炎、血管異常增生、和其他。

